news_header: US continues negotiations with Ukraine despite tensions between Trump and Zelensky over mineral agreements and criticisms.
news_original_title: Trump jatkoi Zelenskyin mollaamista – ”Hän olisi voinut osallistua keskusteluihin, jos olisi halunnut”
news_text: Despite increasing tensions between President Trump and President Zelensky, the US is still negotiating an agreement with Ukraine regarding mineral resources. Trump criticized Zelensky's leadership and mentioned a previous agreement that Ukraine allegedly broke. US Special Envoy Keith Kellogg is visiting Ukraine to discuss the details of a new agreement, emphasizing the importance of constructive cooperation.
